'''Baraguá Municipal Museum''' is a [[museum]] located in [[Baraguá]], [[Cuba]]. It was established on 26 September 1983.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnpc.cult.cu/institucion/553|title=Museo Municipal de Baraguá|publisher=Portal del Consejo Nacional de Patrimonio Cultural|accessdate=2015-11-01}}</ref>

The museum holds collections on history, decorative arts, weaponry, archeology, natural science and numismatics.

