'''''Enciclopedia Combi Visual''''' is an encyclopedia edition printed in [[Barcelona]], [[Spain]] in 1974 composed of 18 volumes.  The first set is coloured red containing five books, the second in white containing 13.  The encyclopedia edition was primarily composed of black and white pictures (many coloured), several are hand drawn.  The contents include subjects such as [[Economics|economy]], [[wildlife]], [[human evolution]], [[colonialism]], [[animal]]s and [[medicine]].

* Format - 17.6 x 24.5&nbsp;cm
* Five books in the red edition contain 2,500 pages.

